[[Image:Terje Riis-Johansen Senterpartiet Landbruks- og matminister20051017.jpg|thumb|right|Terje Riis Johansen]]
'''Terje Riis Johansen''' (b. [[1968]]) is a politician for the [[Norway|Norwegian]] [[Centre Party (Norway)|Centre Party]]. He is currently Minister of Agriculture and Food [[2005]] in the [[second cabinet Stoltenberg]], after being political advisor for the Minister of Finance [[1997]]-[[1999]].

